---
title: Mexican Crumbed Banana Blossom Tacos with Cucumber Salsa & Plant-Based Mayo
description: This versatile fruit with a similar texture to cooked white fish is the perfect plant-based alternative to switch
out with your regular protein. Crumb it with Mexican spices and panko, then stack it into a taco along with
crunchy salad leaves and pickled onion. Time to tick these tacos off the bucket list.

 *This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
